<html>
<body>
Syntax:<br>
<br>
group looter [person]<br>
<br>
Description:<br>
<br>
The leader of the group can appoint a person to do all the looting for<br>
the group - uses that person's autoloot and autoskin options for all<br>
corpses.  Mobs like ghosts, that do not have corpses, will still need to<br>
be looted manually.<br>
</html>
</body>
